headline: 1 Industrials Stock on Our Watchlist and 2 to Question
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Still, their generally high capital requirements expose them to the ups and downs of economic cycles, and the market seems to be baking in a prolonged downturn as the industry has shed 6.6% over the past six months. This performance was worse than the S&P 500’s 1% fall.
